30
0:01:41.33,000 --> 0:01:44,000
I really, really wanted to go to the Arctic.

31
0:01:44.33,000 --> 0:01:46,000
There was something about that place

32
0:01:46.33,000 --> 0:01:48,000
which drew me to it.

33
0:01:48.33,000 --> 0:01:51,000
And, well, sometimes it takes a long time

34
0:01:51.33,000 --> 0:01:53,000
for a dream to come true.

35
0:01:53.33,000 --> 0:01:56,000
