62
0:03:04.33,000 --> 0:03:07,000
Well, swimming across the North Pole,

63
0:03:07.33,000 --> 0:03:1,000
it's not an ordinary thing to do.

64
0:03:10.33,000 --> 0:03:12,000
I mean, just to put it in perspective,

65
