111
0:05:22.33,000 --> 0:05:25,000
I was hyperventilating so much,

112
0:05:25.33,000 --> 0:05:27,000
and within seconds my hands were numb.

113
0:05:27.33,000 --> 0:05:29,000
And it was -- the paradox is

114
0:05:29.33,000 --> 0:05:31,000
that you're in freezing cold water,

115
0:05:31.33,000 --> 0:05:33,000
but actually you're on fire.

116
0:05:33.33,000 --> 0:05:35,000
