117
0:05:35.33,000 --> 0:05:37,000
I remember just trying to get out of the water.

118
0:05:37.33,000 --> 0:05:39,000
I climbed out of the ice.

119
0:05:39.33,000 --> 0:05:42,000
And I remember taking the goggles off my face

120
0:05:42.33,000 --> 0:05:45,000
