131
0:06:18.33,000 --> 0:06:22,000
and trying to defrost my fingers.

132
0:06:22.33,000 --> 0:06:28,000
And I thought, in two days' time, I was going to do this swim across the North Pole.

133
0:06:28.33,000 --> 0:06:32,000
