134
0:06:32.33,000 --> 0:06:34,000
for one kilometer across the North Pole.

135
0:06:34.33,000 --> 0:06:37,000
And this dream which I had had ever since I was a young boy

136
0:06:37.33,000 --> 0:06:4,000
